%N A048902 Indices of heptagonal numbers (A000566) which are also hexagonal.
%C A048902 As n increases, this sequence is approximately geometric with common ratio r = lim_{n->oo} a(n)/a(n-1) = (2 + sqrt(5))^4 = 161 + 72*sqrt(5). - _Ant King_, Dec 26 2011
%D A048902 Elena Deza and Michel Marie Deza, Figurate numbers, World Scientific Publishing (2012), page 39.
